{"tid":866352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，條高鐵執鳩左佢啦","createTime":"2018-10-17T19:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T12:47:42.000Z","uid":63779,"like":293,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0429222ff9b821853da50e0f8a5ead29bdc5c1f5","tid":866352,"uid":63779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T19:51:39.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=qJafdh2PD12xFIro0Oi7zDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=772c9302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】港鐵表示，收到中國鐵路廣州局通知，受鐵路施工工程影響，由11月11日起，往來香港西九龍及上海虹橋的車次G99及G100的行車時間表或有所調整，於上述時間開出的該列車的車票預售服務暫停，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">G99原定每天下午2時10分由上海虹橋出發，晚上10時28分到西九龍</span>；<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">G100則為早上11時10分由西九龍出發，晚上7時27分到達上海</span>。中途站有杭州東、南昌西、長沙南、韶關、廣州南、深圳北等。二等車費為1156港元，一等為1889港元，特等為2168港元，商務為3600港元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBhsLi3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBhsLi3.jpg&h=86ad53ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地3個鐘搞點你老母要成8個鐘，都算，貴又貴撚過人，時間選擇又少撚過人。多成5個鐘夠香港半日遊都得啦，執鳩左佢啦龜鐵。仲話增強競爭力，貴又貴過人，慢又慢過人選擇又少過人，咁都增強到，你不如話可以增加港豬性能力。"},{"pid":"f1b352edf525a3b96dee58a1f97e47711a56f168","tid":866352,"uid":81113,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T20:00:01.000Z","msg":"叫鄭汝樺賠比你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/鄭汝樺\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E9%84%AD%E6%B1%9D%E6%A8%BA&d=qJafdh2PD12xFIro0Oi7zDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=51a053cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/鄭汝樺</a>"},{"pid":"1e93aab83b735238419fae8c4b3842a2f0e1d6b8","tid":866352,"uid":13281,"like":159,"dislike":1,"score":158,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T20:04:26.000Z","msg":"諗起通車果日有個女人話搭飛機去北京要14-15個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b8a51c3e454c668a9435991d2a90d8a3a3dd